00:28:51.372 --> 00:28:52.211
pero no era capaz de

00:28:52.291 --> 00:28:53.732
o no podía hacerlo.

00:28:54.132 --> 00:28:54.451
Chica,

00:28:54.451 --> 00:28:55.691
de hecho,

00:28:56.012 --> 00:28:56.571
no tenía que

00:28:57.691 --> 00:28:58.772
me lo confieso.

